pretty_captioner        A wrapper for the captioner function
pretty_ci               Format an estimate, lower and upper confidence
                        intervals into a single character string
pretty_figref           A wrapper for pretty_captioner with sensible
                        defaults for captioning figures
pretty_inline_ci        Reformat an estimate, with lower/upper
                        confidence/credible intervals with an
                        explanatory note
pretty_per_effect       A Function to Convert Effect Estimates into
                        Percentage Changes
pretty_percentage       Calculate a percentage, and then format for
                        publication
pretty_round            Round and format numeric vectors; standardising
                        trailing zeros
pretty_supfigref        A wrapper for pretty_captioner with sensible
                        defaults for captioning supplementary figures
pretty_suptabref        A wrapper for pretty_captioner with sensible
                        defaults for captioning supplementary tables
pretty_table            Wrapper function for pretty tables
pretty_tabref           A wrapper for pretty_captioner with sensible
                        defaults for captioning tables
